About Us

The Sound Garden is an independent record store operating since 1993. We carry the largest selection of new and used vinyl on the East Coast, as well as CDs, Movies, Turntables, and much more. We are also known for our in-store events from national artists including Post Malone, Noah Kahan, Beach House, Twenty One Pilots, The 1979 and many more.
